Author: Sean Bailey
Co-authors: Koren Nyles, Chris Wilson

This site allows the user to sort posts by boasts, roasts, and likes.
They can open a drop-down menu from the homepage to add a new
post. It opens up a form with the information places needed for 
submitting a post.
Users can vote on posts to determine whether they like it or not.
By default, the posts are sorted by the time in which they were
posted.